text:
Randy and Jenny Boyd are providing a $5.000 grant to support the launch of new social enterprise start-ups in Central Queensland.
Read more about the Randall & Jenny Boyd Grant here.
The Social Enterprise Academy will provide you with:
1-day intensive training program with experienced social entrepreneurs and industry experts;
Access to a community of like-minded individuals who share your passion for creating positive impact;
Ongoing mentorship and support from experienced social entrepreneurs and industry experts; and,
Networking opportunities to connect with potential partners, a nd collaborators.
By participating in the Social Enterprise Academy, you'll gain practical skills and knowledge to develop your idea into a sustainable and impactful social enterprise.
Applications close   26th March 2023!
Don't miss out on this opportunity to take your social enterprise to the next level. Apply now to secure your spot!assistant

**Social Enterprise Academy - Launch Your Impactful Venture!**

Calling all changemakers in Central Queensland!

Are you passionate about addressing social or environmental issues in your community? Do you have an innovative idea that can drive positive change?

We're excited to announce the launch of the Social Enterprise Academy, designed to equip you with the skills, knowledge, and connections needed to turn your vision into a thriving social enterprise.

Thanks to the generous support of Randy and Jenny Boyd, we're offering a limited number of grants worth $5,000 each to support the launch of new social enterprises in Central Queensland.
